<div class="container d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center vh-100">
    <div class="row align-items-center shadow p-4 bg-white rounded w-100" style="max-width: 1000px;">
        <div class="col-md-5 text-center mb-3 mb-md-0">
            <img src="~/images/Profile.png" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="About Us">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="text-primary fw-bold">Privacy</h2>
            <p>At RFST, we take data privacy and security seriously. We are committed to protecting the confidentiality of all information stored on our platform.</p>
