            <p>Doctors using our platform can trust that their information, as well as their patients' data, is protected through stringent security measures. Our systems are designed to maintain the integrity and security of all uploaded medical images and records.</p>
            <p>By using our platform, you acknowledge and agree to our commitment to safeguarding your data and upholding the highest standards of privacy.</p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
